<div id="instruction">
  <div class="modal fade" id="instructions" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content bg-dark">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">How To Play:</h1>
          <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <h3> 1. You Will Be Shown The Definition of a Word From The Dictionary. </h3>
          <p></p>
          <h3> 2. You Will Be Given a Scrambled set of letters that form the word like this. </h3>

          <h3 class="text-center">
            <% icons = ["fa-s", "fa-c", "fa-r", "fa-a", "fa-b", "fa-l", "fa-l", "fa-e", "fa-r"].shuffle %>
            <% icons.each do |icon| %>
              <i class="fa-solid <%= icon %>"></i>
            <% end %>
          </h3>

          <h3> 3. You Will Have 60 Seconds To Unscramble The Letters To Form The Word. </h3>

          <h3 class="text-center">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <% icons = ["fa-s", "fa-c", "fa-r", "fa-a", "fa-b", "fa-l", "fa-l", "fa-e", "fa-r"] %>
            <% icons.each do |icon| %>
              <i class="fa-solid <%= icon %>"></i>
            <% end %>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
          </h3>

          <h3> 4. Each Correct answer will reward you with points! each wrong answer will take away health points</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Understood</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
